{"tid":891742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市第二輪爆煲】90後陳先生：400呎跌到200萬就買！","createTime":"2018-11-06T10:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:01:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e303038c57386427d53f87b676b465fdf32f17cc","tid":891742,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"2018-11-04217.1K<br />\n即時財經<br />\n <br />\n九龍灣地產代理行門口驚現，「第一滴血得寶408萬」的廣告版。90後得寶租客陳先生表示，得寶花園叫價逾400萬，「貴到好唔合理」，即使價格較上月初的成交價跌了約100萬元，他認為只是樓價過往升幅太瘋狂，現時是正常的回調，而且得寶樓齡逾30年，實用面積、間隔及圖則不合個人口味，認為屋苑不僅此價。<br />\n<br />\n他笑指，當得寶花園400方呎單位，跌至200萬元時，便會購入，雖然不太可能發生。他認為樓市受貿易戰及加息等外圍因素，末來1至2年仍然有下調空間，現時不是入市好時機，仍持觀望態度。"},{"pid":"28a9818175d14a8f0e8de1fdf9bb402a015e5896","tid":891742,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"到時銀行都唔借錢<br />\n要full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29aa8c7758c6ab5d790ddde97898de45c25addc5","tid":891742,"uid":25866,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28a9818175d14a8f0e8de1fdf9bb402a015e5896","tid":891742,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"到時銀行都唔借錢<br />\n要full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"衣家比4成<br />\n平 一半有咩分別"},{"pid":"6239301b0cb80c991d327264fb95df50ab9f609b","tid":891742,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29aa8c7758c6ab5d790ddde97898de45c25addc5","tid":891742,"uid":25866,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28a9818175d14a8f0e8de1fdf9bb402a015e5896","tid":891742,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"到時銀行都唔借錢<br />\n要full pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"衣家比4成<br />\n平 一半有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:25